org.hkijena.acaq5.api.parameters

Class ACAQTraversedParameterCollection

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.hkijena.acaq5.api.parameters.ACAQTraversedParameterCollection
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ACAQCustomParameterCollection, ACAQParameterCollection

    public class ACAQTraversedParameterCollection
extends Object
implements ACAQParameterCollection, ACAQCustomParameterCollection
    An ACAQParameterCollection that contains the parameters of one or multiple ACAQParameterCollection instances in a traversed form.
